programme.title: Hilangkah Janji Kita Ep15
programme.desc: Tan Sri Syed akhirnya berkahwin juga dengan Izlyn. Nisa tidak setuju kerana yakin yang Izlyn mempunyai motif jahat untuk membalas dendam.

programme.desc: Ibu Fara tak sudah-sudah menyalahkan Fara kerana masih percaya pada Razlan. Fara yang juga benar kecewa dengan Razlan, kemudian memberitahu ibunya dia sudah ada calon lain. Fara membawa pulang Farid kerana tidak mahu lagi berfikir tentang lelaki sempurna.

programme.desc: Selera Bajet Kali ini Razif akan mencari hidangan - hidangan makanan untuk pagi, petang dan malam di Johor di bawah 20 ringgit. Lokasi episod ini adalah R&H Cafe, Asam Pedas JJ & Mee Badung Muar Udang Galah.

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep07
programme.desc: Airil membuat kejutan membawa sejambak bunga di resort tempat Fatihah bekerja. Lebih memeranjatkan ketika itu Nizam ada bersama Fatihah. Aleya juga begitu teruja melihat kehadiran ayahnya. Pada mulanya hanya Aleya dan Airil meluangkan masa bersama tetapi setelah beberapa kali memujuk Fatihah, akhirnya Fatihah bersetuju mengambil cuti demi Airil dan Aleya. Malangnya, Nizam yang mula cemburu sengaja membuat Fatihah agar tiada masa bersama Airil. Airil yang mengetahui niat Nizam memberinya amaran agar jangan mengganggu Fatihah. Fatihah kecewa melihat kejadian itu menuduh Airil cemburu buta dengan mana-mana lelaki yang cuba mendekatinya. Dia berhak untuk teruskan hidup kalau Airil masih tidak berubah. Ia semakin mencabar Airil. Norlin akhirnya setuju menemukan Arif dengan keluarganya tetapi memberi amaran pada Normah supaya menjaga mulutnya. Sebelum pulang ke kampung, lagi sekali Airil memberi amaran kepada Nizam.

programme.title: Dapur Dara S2 Ep10
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10, Liana Awang, tukang masak Dapur Dara akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat. Untuk episod ini, Liana akan memasak Telur Burung Puyuh Masak Bendi dan Kuih Keria.

programme.title: J.K.K S4 Ep04
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan orang kampung menyambut kedatangan sultan ke Kampung Karut. Sultan ingin mencari sepasang selipar yang hilang di kampung itu serta mencari tuan punya selipar berkenaan. Sultan mempercayai pemilik selipar itu yang pernah menyelamatkan istana dari api yang marak. Setelah pencarian, Pak Kodi yang dikesan sebagai tuan punya selipar dan bakal berkahwin dengan puterinya. Selepas Pak Kodi merayu, sultan setuju membatalkan perkahwinan tersebut dengan syarat Pak Kodi mesti menghantar roti ke puteri setiap hari.

programme.title: Huru Hara S6 Ep04

programme.title: Jangan Benci Cintaku S1 Ep20
programme.desc: Sementara Feka dan Shah berada di Perth, Nenek Shah dan Husna tidak dapat menghubungi Shah atau Feka. Dalam pada itu, Husna datang dengan tiba-tiba. Feka berbual dengan Damia dan memaklumkan dia akan balik ke rumah ibu bapanya setelah dapat izin Shah. Shah yang tiba di rumah ibu bapanya, akui dia silap dan meminta masa untuk dia betulkan kesilapannya. Dia juga berjanji Feka tetap tidak akan diceraikan. Husna bermati matian ingin berehat di rumah Shah, sedangkan Shah tidak mahu dia tinggal di rumah Shah. Keesokan pagi Husna siapkan minum pagi. programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep26
programme.desc: Delisha selamat melahirkan anak di sebuah hospital swasta. Bagi Gayah, dia terpaksa membawa Delisha ke situ kerana dia tahu pasangan itu tidak mampu. Di samping itu, Gayah dan Sabar mendesak memberikan anak mereka sebagai jaminan. Pun begitu, Faiq terpaksa menanda surat janji dengan Gayah. Apabila Faiq bersama isteri dan bayi mereka balik ke rumah, Gayah dan Sabar mendesak Faiq. Delisha terus merayu kepada Gayah, Gayah terus membawa keluar bayi mereka. Dengan usaha Abang Ali, dia dapat menahan semula Gayah dan Sabar, bayi diambil semula kerana resit bayaran ada dengan Abang Ali. Abang Ali menyerahkan bayi itu kepada isteri imam (haji), Kak Anum. Dia kemudiannya membawa bayi itu ke pangkuan Delisha dan Faiq. Sebelum itu melalui Abang Ali, Faiq telah diperkenalkan kepada Datuk Sofia, Faiq ditemuduga dan akhirnya diterima sebagai eksekutif disyarikatnya. Syarikat datuk berkaitan dengan perniagaan reka bentuk dan fesyen. Faiq kemudiannya juga membawa Delisha untuk diperkenalkan kepada datuk kerana Delisha berkemahiran di bidang itu .Suatu hari di pertengahan Delisha sedang asyik menerangkan sesuatu, tiba-tiba Nenda, Datuk Rosnah, ibu dan bapa Faiq dan ibu bapa Delisha dituruti Ustaz Ghazali.

programme.title: J.K.K S4 Ep05
programme.desc: Cikgu Murni datang ke Kampung Kalut untuk mewar-warkan pertandingan pantun antara kampung sebelah iaitu Kampung Sendu. Juara pantun Kampung Sendu iaitu Awang Champion ada membuat kunjungan ke Kampung Kalut dan saja mengintai aktiviti latihan pantun Kampung Kalut. Cikgu Murni dan Awang Champion sebenarnya saling mengenali tetapi mereka berpura-pura tidak mengenali kerana ingin membuat perancangan jahat supaya Kampung Kalut kalah. Cikgu Murni dalam diam telah membuat ramuan minuman untuk Pak Din dan Pak Kodi sakit tekak supaya mereka tidak boleh mengeluarkan suara ketika bertanding. Tibanya hari pertandingan, Pak Din dan Pak Kodi kehilangan suara dan pertandingan pantun hampir dibatalkan. Awang Champion berasa sangat gembira. Tetapi, Lola dan Kojack telah membawa bukti perbualan plan jahat mereka.

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep04
programme.desc: Airil merasa tergugat lantas melarikan Aleya dan menginap di sebuah hotel. Fatihah panik mencari Aleya di serata tempat. Dia cuba bertanyakan pada Normah tetapi diherdik dan dihalau. Normah yang membenci Fatihah menyokong penuh tindakan Airil melarikan Aleya. Pak Jalal tiba meredakan keadaan. Ibu bapa Fatihah menasihatinya agar beralah kerana Airil mungkin tidak sanggup berjauhan dengan Aleya. Fatihah mengugutuntuk mengambil tindakan mahkamah menuntut hak penjagaan anak tetapi Airil tidak peduli dan mahu Fatihah pindah seorang diri. Berikutan itu Airil mengambil cuti panjang namun dia terus dipecat. Dia hampir menumbuk majikannya di hadapan Aleya namun Fatihah muncul membawa Aleya pergi. Atas nasihat Pak Jalal, Airil merelakan hati melepaskan Fatihah dan Aleya ke Terengganu. Fatihah turut meminta maaf atas kejadian yang berlaku. Malam itu merekameluangkan masa bersama. Fatihah sebak lalu beredar tatkala Airil sedang mendendangkan lagu buatnya

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep05
programme.desc: Hidup Airil tidak keruan sejak beberapa bulan dia berenggang dengan Fatihah dan Aleya yang telah berhijrah ke Terengganu. Airil masih tidak berputus asa memujuk Fatihah untuk rujuk semula. Airil seolah gila talak. Aleya pula menghadapi kesukaran bertutur loghat Terengganu. Dia berkali cuba memujuk Fatihah untuk pulang ke kampung bertemu ayahnya untuk melepaskan rindu tetapi Fatihah berkeras hati. Namun Fatihah sering teringat saat-saat Airil sentiasa berada di sisinya ketika dia dalam kesukaran dan waktu bahagia mereka. Dalam pada itu, Nizam cuba mengambil kesempatan mendekati Fatihah. Ketika pulang Fatihah dan Aleya pulang ke rumah, tayar kereta mereka pancit. Bersambung

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep06
programme.desc: Fatihah cuba menghubungi Nizam tetapi gagal dan dia terpaksa menukar tayar sendiri. Airil yang mengetahui hal itu panik kerana tidak dapat berbuat apa-apa. Ibunya Normah pula tidak putus-putus berprasangka hubungan sulit suaminya dengan Kiah. Jalal semakin muak dengan peel isterinya. Aleeya kini sudah pandai memberontak sebab merindui ayahnya dan tertekan kerana Fatihah lebih banyak meluangkan masa di tempat kerja. Fatihah mula merasakan kepayahan hidup tanpa seorang suami. Airil terdengar keluhan mereka dan membuat keputusan untuk ke Terengganu. Panggilan dan SMS Airil bertalu-talu membuatkan Fatihah hilang fokus di tempat kerja. Oleh itu, Nizam mengalu-alukan Fatihah jika mahu menjadikannya teman untuk bergantung. Airil yang baru tiba di resort itu terkedu mendengar perbualan mereka.

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep07
programme.desc: Airil membuat kejutan membawa sejambak bunga di resort tempat Fatihah bekerja. Lebih memeranjatkan ketika itu Nizam ada bersama Fatihah. Aleya juga begitu teruja melihat kehadiran ayahnya. Pada mulanya hanya Aleya dan Airil meluangkan masa bersama tetapi setelah beberapa kali memujuk Fatihah, akhirnya Fatihah bersetuju mengambil cuti demi Airil dan Aleya. Malangnya, Nizam yang mula cemburu sengaja membuat Fatihah agar tiada masa bersama Airil. Airil yang mengetahui niat Nizam memberinya amaran agar jangan mengganggu Fatihah. Fatihah kecewa melihat kejadian itu menuduh Airil cemburu buta dengan mana-mana lelaki yang cuba mendekatinya. Dia berhak untuk teruskan hidup kalau Airil masih tidak berubah. Ia semakin mencabar Airil. Norlin akhirnya setuju menemukan Arif dengan keluarganya tetapi memberi amaran pada Normah supaya menjaga mulutnya. Sebelum pulang ke kampung, lagi sekali Airil memberi amaran kepada Nizam.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep03
programme.desc: Memaparkan Puan Yasmin menawarkan kepada menantunya Sofia butik perniagaan yang ditutup sementara waktu untuk beliau memulakan perniagaan. Majlis resepsi dijangkakan dalam beberapa hari lagi, namun keluarga Sofia masih tidak mendapat jemputan. Ini menimbulkan curiga pada Sofia. Semasa berada dalam dewan resepsi, Amar ternampak kad jemputan perkahwinan majlis tersebut tercatat nama pengantin Amar dan Erina. Apabila Amar bertanya ibunya, Yasmin mahu anaknya menunaikan janjinya sebelum ini dan terpaksa mengikut kehendak ibunya. Erina tiba dari UK kerana majlis persandingan akan diadakan pada keesokan harinya. Amar dalam perjalanan balik bertemu Sofia, dia telah dipukul sehingga pengsan oleh orang suruhan Yasmin. Yasmin bertemu dengan Sofia, memberitahu mengenai mengenai pernikahan Erina dengan Amar. Sofia bersedih kerana Amar tidak pulang-pulang dan gagal dihubungi. Erina mulai syak sesuatu yang tidak baik mengenai perkahwinan mereka. Di akhir episod, Rusdi melawat Amar di hospital setelah diselamatkan apabila dijumpai pengsan. Mereka mengetahui rahsia majlis perkahwinan yang sedang dirancang oleh ibunya.

programme.title: Pengantin 100 Hari Ep04
programme.desc: Memaparkan Yasmin Sofia setelah dia melarikan diri selepas diberitahu Amar akan dikahwinkan dengan Erina dalam majlis yang dirancang olehnya. Amar dan bapanya merasa tersinggung dengan penipuan oleh ibunya, Rusdi terusan memarahi isterinya kerana memaksa Amar berkahwin dengan Erina dan menipu mereka tanpa memikirkan perasaan ahli keluarganya. Rusdi meminta orang-orangnya mencari Sofia yang telah menghilangkan diri. Amar masih lagi tidak sihat, namun Yasmin mahu majlis perkahwinan Amar dengan Erina dalam tempoh dua jam lagi. Ramai tetamu yang hadir, Iqbal turut hadir kerana mewakili majikannya Tan Sri Ibrahim di majlis perkahwinan tersebut. Melihat Amar sedang bersanding, Iqbal terus menumbuk Amar. Ini menimbulkan kemarahan Datuk Fahmi dan meminta penjelasan dari Yasmin. Namun Erina bersedia untuk menjadi madu Sofia, namun Amar keluar mencari Sofia.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep03
programme.desc: Ibu shira dapat rasakan Shira dilamun cinta kerana sanggup cuba makan budu. Cuti pertengahan semester bermula dan Faizul balik ke Kelantan. Setibanya di rumah dia terkejut Mek Yan Mek Yan marah Atikah teruk sebab difitnah orang kampung. Faizul meminta Mek Yan izinkan sahaja Atikah berkahwin dengan Mat Yie. Faizul dapat panggilan, teruja sangat apabila tahu Shira dekat Kota Bahru. Shira sanggup tipu semua orang konon ada urusan bisnes semata-mata mahu jumpa Faizul. Mereka seronok luangkan masa bersama dan perasaan mereka semakin mendalam. Faizul jemput shira ke rumahnya. Mek Yan bimbang Shira moden tak bertudung berbanding Pia, anak Tok Imam yang dia mahu jodohkan dengan Faizul.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep04
programme.desc: Tangan Faizul retak dan ditahan di wad akibat kemalangan. Dari luar wad, Shira terdengar Faizul sedang video call dengan seseorang. Shira gelisah dan tanya Arman. Katanya, itu Sha, mungkin kekasih Faizul. Semester depan, Sha akan balik semula ke kampus. Selepas dua hari di wad, Arman hantar Faizul balik ke Kelantan yang dapat cuti sakit. Di KL, Shira nyatakan hasratnya mahu meminang Faizul. Datuk Badrul menentang tetapi akhirnya setuju. Faizul dan Mek Yan terkejut dengan kehadiran Shira sekeluarga. Faizul yang tahu bisnes berjaya tambat hati Datuk Badrul sehingga beliau setuju meminang Faizul. Mek Yan marah Faizul, perempuan di situ tak ada yang meminang lelaki. Namun, akhirnya Mek Yan restu hubungan itu tetapi biar mereka yang datang meminang Shira. Pertunangan pun berlangsung

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep26
programme.desc: Delisha selamat melahirkan anak di sebuah hospital swasta. Bagi Gayah, dia terpaksa membawa Delisha ke situ kerana dia tahu pasangan itu tidak mampu. Di samping itu, Gayah dan Sabar mendesak memberikan anak mereka sebagai jaminan. Pun begitu, Faiq terpaksa menanda surat janji dengan Gayah. Apabila Faiq bersama isteri dan bayi mereka balik ke rumah, Gayah dan Sabar mendesak Faiq. Delisha terus merayu kepada Gayah, Gayah terus membawa keluar bayi mereka. Dengan usaha Abang Ali, dia dapat menahan semula Gayah dan Sabar, bayi diambil semula kerana resit bayaran ada dengan Abang Ali. Abang Ali menyerahkan bayi itu kepada isteri imam (haji), Kak Anum. Dia kemudiannya membawa bayi itu ke pangkuan Delisha dan Faiq. Sebelum itu melalui Abang Ali, Faiq telah diperkenalkan kepada Datuk Sofia, Faiq ditemuduga dan akhirnya diterima sebagai eksekutif disyarikatnya. Syarikat datuk berkaitan dengan perniagaan reka bentuk dan fesyen. Faiq kemudiannya juga membawa Delisha untuk diperkenalkan kepada datuk kerana Delisha berkemahiran di bidang itu .Suatu hari di pertengahan Delisha sedang asyik menerangkan sesuatu, tiba-tiba Nenda, Datuk Rosnah, ibu dan bapa Faiq dan ibu bapa Delisha dituruti Ustaz Ghazali.

programme.title: Terowong Ep6
programme.desc: Episod 6, bertajuk ' Surat' ini mengisahkan Ramli yang ingin memiliki harta bapa mentuanya telah membuat perjanjian dalam sekeping surat dengan seorang tua yang dijumpainya di dalam terowong semasa dia berjoging. Setelah dia berjaya,Ramli telah dihantui dengan tuntutan janji orang tua tersebut supaya Ramli membawa darah manusia untuk semahan di dalam terowong itu. Dalam pada itu dengan pertolongan bekas kekasihnya, isteri Ramli telah meminta pertolongan seorang bomoh (orang tua) yang sama untuk mengatasi masalah Ramli yang suka bermain kayu tiga. Malangnya dengan hasutan bomoh tersebut Ramli yang cemburu terhadap isterinya dengan rakan sepejabatnya itu telah membunuh mereka berdua. Bomoh itu juga telah berpesan kepada Ramli supaya membawa korban kepadanya dan dua tahun kemudian, Ramli membawa kekasihnya pula untuk dikorbankan tetapi kali ini Ramli sendiri turut menjadi korban bomoh tersebut

programme.title: The Dawn
programme.desc: Berikutan pembunuhan keluarganya di tangan bapanya, seorang wanita muda dihantar untuk tinggal di sebuah biara. Tetapi syaitan yang melanda ayahnya mengikuti, membangkitkan semula mimpi buruk masa lalunya.

programme.title: Nang Nak
programme.desc: Seorang lelaki pulang ke rumah dari berperang di mana isteri dan anaknya menyambutnya dengan penuh semangat. Tetapi ada sesuatu yang tidak menyenangkan tentang isterinya yang cuba disampaikan oleh rakan karibnya dan orang yang baik kepadanya.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep3
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Hunter Killer
programme.desc: Kapal selam kelas Los Angeles AS USS Tampa Bay hilang ketika membayangi kapal selam kelas Akula Rusia Konek di Artik. Laksamana Muda John Fisk (Common) menghantar kapal selam kelas Virginia USS Arkansas, di bawah perintah Komander Joe Glass (Gerard Butler) yang baru dinaikkan pangkat dan tidak ortodoks untuk menyiasat. Pada masa yang sama, pasukan Navy SEAL di bawah pimpinan Leftenan Bill Beaman dihantar untuk memerhatikan pangkalan tentera laut Rusia secara diam-diam. Apabila mereka tiba di pangkalan tentera laut, mereka menyaksikan menteri pertahanan Dmitri Durov melakukan rampasan kuasa dan menawan Presiden Rusia Zakarin, dan dengan cepat menyedari bahawa Durov berhasrat untuk mencetuskan perang.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Episod terakhir yang mengisahkan Pak Bado dijumpai mati dibunuh. Disebabkan ini, Ramdi telah memberitahu Ustaz Hambali apa yang berlaku kepada Sarakit yang dirogol dan kemudiannya dibunuh Pak Bado. Ustaz Hambali telah berusaha menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi dengan memulihkan semangat Rafiq dan menghalau jin Sarakit dari badan Dina. Akibatnya Dina telah meninggal dunia. Dengan bantuan orang-orang kampung, mereka berjaya berjumpa kubur Sarakit dan Rafiq redha dengan apa yang berlaku terhadap Sarakit. Rafiq meninggalkan kampung dan Ramdi kemudiannya menjadi buta apabila terjatuh mencederakan matanya.

programme.title: Chikaro
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Two Cops Ep16
programme.desc: Cha Dong Tak ialah seorang polis yang mempunyai rasa keadilan yang kuat. Pada suatu hari semasa memburu seorang penjenayah, tubuhnya secara tidak dapat dijelaskan telah dirasuk oleh jiwa seorang penipu yang licik Gong Soo Chang. Dua jiwa antagonis berakhir dalam perkongsian penyelesaian jenayah yang pelik. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang wartawan impulsif, Song Ji An, menyertai siasatan.

programme.title: Hikayat Merong Mahawangsa
programme.desc: Pada tahun 120, Empayar Rom ketika itu di bawah pemerintahan Hadrian sementara di negara China, Dinasti Han merupakan sebuah empayar yang kuat dan telah memperluaskan pemerintahannya ke negara Asia Tengah. Semasa angkatan Rom sedang membaik pulih kapal mereka di Goa, mereka meminta pertolongan Merong Mahawangsa mengiringi Putera Rom ke Langkasuka (dikatakan terletak di utara Malaysia) untuk berkahwin dengan seorang Puteri China yang cantik dari Dinasti Han.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Awang berpuas hati kerana 2 mangsa sudah berjaya dikorbankan. Long Hussain yang masih segar dan bertenaga berjaya dipergunakan Awang dengan baik. Bila Awang mengesan mangsanya, roh Awang akan bersatu dengan jasad Long Hussain. Kali ini mangsanya adalah Mira, seorang usahawan andaman dan butik perkahwinan yang bekerja sendiri di rumah. Mira tinggal dengan kedua orang tuanya sementara adik beradiknya yang lain di Kuala Lumpur. Ketika orang tua Mira ke Kuala Lumpur Mira tinggal bersendirian. Mira diserang dan dibunuh oleh pocong.

programme.title: Lampor: Keranda Terbang
programme.desc: Edwin dan Netta bersama dua anak mereka, Agam dan Sekar, kembali ke kampung Netta di Temanggung. Kampung yang telah ditinggal Netta 25 tahun bersama ibunya yang marah akan perbuatan sesat ayahnya. Netta harus menyampaikan pesan terakhir almarhumah untuk ayahnya. Netta disambut curiga dan dianggap pembawa musibah karena kampungnya sedang dilanda teror Lampor, setan pencabut nyawa yang membawa keranda terbang.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep7
programme.desc: Akil yang sedang tidur telah dijejutkan oleh saka Kimchi yang menuntut dia menolongnya pulang ke Korea. Menurut Kimchi Akil telah menolong tiga daripada kawannya iaitu Jendul, Big Foot dan Mayang Kasturi dan kali ini giliran dia pula ditolong. Akil ingin tahu bagaimana Kimchi boleh sampai kemari. Mengikut Kimchi dia datang bersama tuannya tetapi tuannya meninggal kerana tercekek tulang semasa makan di sebuah restoran. Kerana tiada bertuan, dia terus tinggal di retoran itu dan mengacau pengunjung restoran. Tuan punya restoran telah mengupah Bomoh Tok Misai untuk menghalaunya. Tok Misai telah menangkapnya dan sejak itu dia diperhambakan oleh Tok Misai hinggalah To Misai meninggal. Akil masukkan Kimchi kedalam suatu kotak dan menghantarnya ke Korea melaui pos laju. Sehingga masa ini, ke empat-empat saka itu iaitu Jendol, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Kimchi telah dibebaskan daripada kekuasaan Tok Misai. Kimchi yang sepatunya berlepas ke Korea telah keluar daripada bungkusan dan datang semula berkumpul dengan tiga teman sakanya. Akil tidak tahu yang Kimchi tidak berangkat ke Korea. Akil berharap dia tidak lagi diganggu oleh empat saka itu.

programme.title: Plan B Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Que dan Mica, pada mulanya tidak bersetuju Khai menerima cadangan daripada seorang pelajar kolej, Airis untuk mencuri kereta, namun setelah Khai memberi alasannya, mereka bukan mahu terlibat secara serius dalam aktiviti itu, tetapi semata-mata sebagai hiburan sahaja, kemudian Que dan Mica bersetuju. Sementara King yang terlibat dalam penyeludupan kereta mewah ke sempadan Thailand, sedang merancang sesuatu bersama-sama pembantunya untuk mengubah strategi mereka supaya tidak terperangkap dalam sekatan polis.

Tok Misai telah menangkapnya dan sejak itu dia diperhambakan oleh Tok Misai hinggalah To Misai meninggal. Akil masukkan Kimchi kedalam suatu kotak dan menghantarnya ke Korea melaui pos laju. Sehingga masa ini, ke empat-empat saka itu iaitu Jendol, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Kimchi telah dibebaskan daripada kekuasaan Tok Misai. Kimchi yang sepatunya berlepas ke Korea telah keluar daripada bungkusan dan datang semula berkumpul dengan tiga teman sakanya. Akil tidak tahu yang Kimchi tidak berangkat ke Korea. Akil berharap dia tidak lagi diganggu oleh empat saka itu.

programme.title: Fist of Stardom
programme.desc: Seorang pemuda yang suka seni mempertahankan diri. Mengembara ke ibu kota untuk mengejar impian ingin menjadi pahlawan, Thongpoon harus menghadapi kumpulan mafia, pertempuran dan pelbagai bidang. Thongpoon mendapat idea untuk membuat filem

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Awang berpuas hati kerana 2 mangsa sudah berjaya dikorbankan. Long Hussain yang masih segar dan bertenaga berjaya dipergunakan Awang dengan baik. Bila Awang mengesan mangsanya, roh Awang akan bersatu dengan jasad Long Hussain. Kali ini mangsanya adalah Mira, seorang usahawan andaman dan butik perkahwinan yang bekerja sendiri di rumah. Mira tinggal dengan kedua orang tuanya sementara adik beradiknya yang lain di Kuala Lumpur. Ketika orang tua Mira ke Kuala Lumpur Mira tinggal bersendirian. Mira diserang dan dibunuh oleh pocong.

programme.title: Kepong Gangster 2
programme.desc: Seorang bekas ahli kumpulan gangster cuba meninggalkan kehidupan lamanya sebagai seorang anggota gangster untuk hidup aman bersama dengan teman wanitanya telah bekerja sebagai seorang mekanik kereta.

programme.title: Plan B Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Que dan Mica, pada mulanya tidak bersetuju Khai menerima cadangan daripada seorang pelajar kolej, Airis untuk mencuri kereta, namun setelah Khai memberi alasannya, mereka bukan mahu terlibat secara serius dalam aktiviti itu, tetapi semata-mata sebagai hiburan sahaja, kemudian Que dan Mica bersetuju. Sementara King yang terlibat dalam penyeludupan kereta mewah ke sempadan Thailand, sedang merancang sesuatu bersama-sama pembantunya untuk mengubah strategi mereka supaya tidak terperangkap dalam sekatan polis.

programme.title: Nang Nak
programme.desc: Seorang lelaki pulang ke rumah dari berperang di mana isteri dan anaknya menyambutnya dengan penuh semangat. Tetapi ada sesuatu yang tidak menyenangkan tentang isterinya yang cuba disampaikan oleh rakan karibnya dan orang yang baik kepadanya.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep5
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Chikaro
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Terowong Ep6
programme.desc: Episod 6, bertajuk ' Surat' ini mengisahkan Ramli yang ingin memiliki harta bapa mentuanya telah membuat perjanjian dalam sekeping surat dengan seorang tua yang dijumpainya di dalam terowong semasa dia berjoging. Setelah dia berjaya,Ramli telah dihantui dengan tuntutan janji orang tua tersebut supaya Ramli membawa darah manusia untuk semahan di dalam terowong itu. Dalam pada itu dengan pertolongan bekas kekasihnya, isteri Ramli telah meminta pertolongan seorang bomoh (orang tua) yang sama untuk mengatasi masalah Ramli yang suka bermain kayu tiga. Malangnya dengan hasutan bomoh tersebut Ramli yang cemburu terhadap isterinya dengan rakan sepejabatnya itu telah membunuh mereka berdua. Bomoh itu juga telah berpesan kepada Ramli supaya membawa korban kepadanya dan dua tahun kemudian, Ramli membawa kekasihnya pula untuk dikorbankan tetapi kali ini Ramli sendiri turut menjadi korban bomoh tersebut

programme.title: Plan B Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai menjalani latihan teknik mencuri kereta-kereta mewah daripada EncikBoon dan disaksikan oleh Airis dan Mica. Sementara itu, Que ketika dalam tahanan, telah memberi informasi kepada polis mengenai kegiatan lumba kereta haram oleh ketua kumpulan, Jim. Que telah dibebaskan, setelah dijamin oleh ibunya dan dia berjanji untuk tidak terlibat dalam aktiviti haram yang dilakukan oleh kawan-kawannya. Dalam satu serbuan pihak polis telah berjaya memberkas salah seorang daripada kumpulan lumba haram itu.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Tom yum goong (2005) ialah filem Thai,Inggeris,Mandarin,Vietnam. Prachya Pinkaew telah mengarahkan filem ini. Tony Jaa,Nathan Jones,Xing Jin,Petchtai Wongkamlao adalah pelakon filem ini. Ia telah dikeluarkan pada tahun 2005. Tom yum goong (2005) dianggap sebagai salah satu filem Aksi, Jenayah, Drama, Thriller terbaik di India dan di seluruh dunia.

programme.title: Kad Cinta
programme.desc: TK mencintai Julia, seorang pelajar universiti di Istanbul. Pertemuan mereka di lapangan terbang Istanbul menimbulkan bibit-bibit cinta. Ingin menampung perbelanjaan kajian, TK pulang ke Malaysia dan bekerja sebagai penghantar surat. Ketika menghantar bungkusan, TK bertemu kembali dengan Julia. Sejak itu, Julia sering menerima kad misteri daripada seorang peminat. Berjayakah Julia membongkar persoalan siapakah yang sering menghantar kad misteri tersebut?

programme.title: Ali Setan 2
programme.desc: Ikatan yang ingin tercipta terpaksa dileraikan kerana campur tangan keluarga menyebabkan Ali dan Asmidar pergi membawa haluan sendiri. Rancangan untuk mendirikan rumahtangga telah diganggu oleh Jeff yang inginkan Asmidar. Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

programme.title: Debu Debu Kasih
programme.desc: Suzana baru pulang dari Amerika dengan membawa ijazah dalam bidang muzik. Dia mengikut kawannya Linda untuk bercuti di Terengganu. Di Terengganu, Suzana berkenalan dengan Hassan – seorang pemuda yang suka menghabiskan masa dengan memerhatikan orang di jeti sambil bermain gitar. Suzana akhirnya membantu Hassan sehingga menjadi seorang penyanyi yang berjaya dan telah jatuh cinta dengan Hassan. Namun Suzana telah dikejutkan dengan perubahan sikap Hassan secara tiba-tiba.

programme.title: KLU
programme.desc: Maria, pelajar universiti di luar negara pulang ke tanahair kerana ayahnya yang sakit menyambung semula pelajarannya secara tempatan. Mengetahui tentang itu, Tuan Hudson yang semakin muflis mengatur langkah untuk memastikan anaknya, Bob mendekatkan dirinya dengan Maria demi harta.

programme.title: Sate

programme.desc: Seorang putera raja bernama Hussein menemui cinta bersama seorang gadis biasa. Namun dia dijodohkan bersama Puteri Balqis. programme.desc: Amelia menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fandy setelah mereka bertemu secara tidak sengaja di Cameron Highlands. Dalam masa yang sama ibu Amelia ingin menjodohkannya dengan Jefri. Fandy berasa bersalah kerana menganggap dirinya punca keluarga Amelia berantakan. Fandy mengambil keputusan untuk membawa diri ke luar negara dan hal ini telah menyebabkan Amelia terpaksa mengahwini Jefri. Selepas berkahwin, Amelia dijangkiti HIV daripada suaminya. Apabila Fandy mengetahui keadaan sebenar, dia ingin menebus segala kesalahannya terhadap Amelia.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep959960
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: Stylish Man-The Chef (M) Ep3360
programme.desc: <Stylish Man – The Chef> is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng, Bernice Tsai and Genie Chuo, together with two professional chefs, A-Chi and James. There are two main themes for the program, which are “Big Stars Come to Cook” and “Five-Star Cooking Show”. <Stylish Man – The Chef> containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: New Taiwan Go (M) Ep2578
programme.desc: Depth analysis of the day breaking news headlines to restore the truth inside

programme.desc: As an ordinary girl, working an ordinary job, at an ordinary convenience store, Lin An An had only one dream in life: to find a good, stable, government job so she could support her aging grandfather. With that single dream in mind, An An never even thought of becoming anything more than the ordinary girl she had always been. But all that changed the day You Yuan Le walked into her life.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep808809
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: The Borderless World (M) Ep658
programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep435
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Young Days No Fears(M) Ep1011
programme.desc: The six girls, as good friends, have gone through their difficulties and crises in relationship, at work, and in their marriage together. Despite many challenges in life, they are not afraid. They have got each other’s back.

programme.title: MMA Diva
programme.desc: Xin Lan takes over her father’s MMA club which is heavily in debt due to poor business. After He Hua defeated Xin Lan, she replaces her to become the new top MMA Diva and challenges Xin Lan’s MMA club to a duel. As Xin Lan is injured, she seeks help from a retried MMA superstar to fight the battle on her behalf to reclaim the club’s and her honour.

programme.title: Love on a Diet
programme.desc: Mini's broken heart leads her to pack on the pounds. She meets an obese man named Fatso who helps her get back on track and shed the pounds. After dropping the unwanted heft, Mini rekindles her relationship with her first love, but is this the happy ending that she wants?

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Push and Shove
programme.desc: A puppy gets gravely injured while defending them from the neighbor's large and aggressive Tibetan Mastiff. The arrogant owner of the Tibetan Mastiff, however, refuses to take responsibility, and the police aren't of much help since no people were hurt. When push comes to shove, the puppy’s owner vows to fight for justice for his dog.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kong’s legendary detective?

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Chang’s first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunt’s puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: American Dreams in China
programme.desc: During the economic reform period in the 80’s, three undergraduates are brought together by a common ambition – to live the American dream.

programme.title: Murderer
programme.desc: A police officer Tai is found seriously hurt while another officer Ling is found lying in a coma at the crime scene. Ling awakens with a memory loss and cannot explain why he was at the scene. As a result, he is accused of attempted murder. While Ling feels aggrieved, he also finds all evidences pointing to him as the murderer...

programme.title: Fearless
programme.desc: This movie is inspired by the true story of real-life hero Huo Yuan Jia. When a fight destroys the reputation of this renowned martial arts champion along with the lives of his family, Huo’s path to redemption brings him face-to-face with the most ferocious opponents in the world.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriend’s wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge – will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: Integrity
programme.desc: Anti-corruption senior officer Chen lines up a key witness, corporate accountant Jack, to testify against a tobacco trading company CEO for bribing high-level customs officer as well as smuggling contraband cigarettes. When neither Jack nor the CEO shows up on the day of the hearing, Chen must team up with his ex-wife to launch an investigation.

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: Directed by renowned director Zhang Yimou, the film is set during the Cultural Revolution, where a common man escapes a labour camp to find a newsreel that captures his daughter for one second in a movie. On the way, he encounters an orphan who also seeks the movie reel. Can the man finally pass the reel to a projectionist and screen the movie?

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Eva’s mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mother’s wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Eva’s heart?

programme.title: Reset
programme.desc: Scientist Xia Tian's hard work finally pays off when she successfully sends living tissue back through time by 110 minutes. When her son dies at the hands of kidnappers, she sends herself back through time on a frantic mission to prevent his death.

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the minister’s conspiracy…

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home; an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death; the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: A Writer's Odyssey
programme.desc: Based on a novel of the same name, this is the story about a father who must kill a novelist in order to find his missing daughter. Through a strange twist of fate, the fantasy world of the novel begins to impact life in the real world.

programme.title: Men on the Dragon
programme.desc: When massive layoffs are expected, four middle-aged men pledge their loyalty to the company by joining the newly formed dragon boat team. As the four embark on their rigorous training, they are forced to face their respective mid-life issues. The process rekindles their long-lost fighting spirit, and they begin to welcome life’s challenges.

programme.title: The Golden Monk
programme.desc: A monk realizes he is the reincarnation of Golden Child who was cast down from heaven to experience life and death a hundred times, as he broke a sacred rule by falling in love with a fairy, Jade. While his memories are erased, Jade refuses to forget their love and accumulates goodwill over a hundred reincarnations to end Golden Child’s suffering.

programme.title: Operation Bangkok
programme.desc: A military veteran, Wu Wei and an undercover cop, Tian Ming lead a team to rescue the hostages captured by a band of thugs in an island outside of Bangkok. As they are about to leave after the rescue, Wu finds that his daughter is also kidnapped, and decides to stay on with Ming to fight the thugs and save her.

programme.title: Sound of Colors
programme.desc: Lonesome marriage consultant Ming meets a blind but charming young lady, Yeuk, at a subway station. When Ming suddenly turns blind too, Yeuk helps him navigate through his world of darkness, and they begin to fall in love. This feature is based on the illustrated book from famous Taiwan illustrator Jimmy Liao.

programme.title: Nezha
programme.desc: A former top team racing driver wants to prove himself in a race but accidentally hurts his teammate Lily, leading to the team’s downfall. When an inexperienced virtual car racing champion joins the team and unexpectedly shines in a real-life race, can the three drivers team up to regain glory for their team?

programme.title: The Grand Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ma Fei Lung, a Chinese martial arts grandmaster, lost everything after he is floored by a former female boxing champion, Chan Tsang. The relevant video was posted on social media and he became the laughing stock of everyone. To reclaim his reputation, Fei Lung challenges Chan Tsang to a rematch. Who will be the winner?

programme.title: The Thousand Faces of Dunjia
programme.desc: A young constable unwittingly gets involved with a secret organization named Wu Yin Men, where all members have supernatural abilities and have protected mankind for centuries. When he learns that mysterious demons with power to destroy the world are increasing, the adventure to hunt them down with Wu Yin Men begins!

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: Love · Revolution
programme.desc: Ai Yoshida will do anything for love, including traveling to Thailand with her boyfriend from Japan to run dope. When her boyfriend is kidnapped by the local gangster after a brawl at a bar, Ai sets out on a rescue mission that sends her on an action-packed roller-coaster ride where she meets a professional assassin who breaks out of jail for love.

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chef’s delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the country’s energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: How to Choose a Royal Bride
programme.desc: The Empress Dowager has arranged young and eligible women for Emperor Kangxi‘s selection. Kangxi is uninterested and becomes bored with the process. He decides to travel incognito as a businessman around the country when he meets Nalan Qiong Yao, who disguises herself as a man to avoid a possible arranged marriage with the Emperor…

programme.title: Kid From Kwangtung
programme.desc: After many years as a respected actor (The Chinese Boxer) and action choreographer (Jackie Chan's Drunken Master), the Shaw Studio finally gave the dependable and commendable Hsu Hsia a chance to direct his own movies. He didn't waste the opportunity, inviting three other kung-fu designers to help on this fight-filled thriller. Wang Yu, co-star of such classics as Dirty Ho and The Kid With A Tattoo, here takes center stage as a young rascal caught between an anti-Ching Confederation and violent, vengeful Ching troops. But when he discovers that the good guys are led by master martial arts actor Jen Shih-kuan (Once Upon A Time In China) and the bad guys are led by the incredible Huang Cheng-li (Snake In The Eagle's Shadow) everyone knows that loads of great kung-fu is in store.

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: Godfather of Canton
programme.desc: Commissioner Liu Ta-hua (Tsao Ta-hua) is arrested by special envoy Cheng Chih-cheng (Wang Jung) for corruption. Coolie Lin Szu-hai (Gordon Liu Chia-hui), who has unintentionally helped Cheng, is given a small post under Lo. Lin is smart and soon learns how to get dockside bribes. Later, he gets a regular spin-off from Adjutant Chang…

programme.title: The House of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: The Shadow Boxer
programme.desc: Skilled shadow Tai Chi boxer Ku Ting hides his skills by working as a construction worker. However, when the thugs assaulted his girlfriend, Ku Ting has no choice but to use his kung fu to show his enemies what it takes to keep justice in line.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends’ help.

programme.title: Death Duel
programme.desc: Third Master is a renowned swordsman in the martial arts world, but the constant challenges by other swordsmen compel him to fake his death and pursue a secluded life. This does not prevent others from seeking him out to challenge him however, and he is forced to return to fight his way till the end.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: Rivals of Kung Fu
programme.desc: Everyone wants to win the annual Lion Dance Trophy, including Wong Fei Hung. His jealous rivals, led by Master Shen, try to frame Wong by placing a decomposed corpse in his Po Chi Lam clinic. This gives Lu Wei, a corrupted cop, the chance to pile Wong Fei Hung with various criminal charges. Will Wong be able to defeat his enemies once again?

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: The Cave of Silken Web
programme.desc: In this third instalment of Shaw Brother’s Journey to the West, Monk Tang San Zang (Ho Fan) is trapped by seven seductive spiders, hell-bent on achieving immortality by eating him! Monkey (Chou Lung Chang), Pigsy (Peng Peng) and Sha Wu Jing (Tien Shun) have to fight with the spiders to rescue Monk Tang San Zang.

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: Constantly being abused by her cruel husband, the frail Chan Sau Ying awaits death from tuberculosis. The new servant girl Yi Wah, takes pity on her mistress’ plight and the pair proceed to drown him one evening. They dump his body in a nearby pond but Sau Ying believes that the man’s bloated corpse has risen from the bog to seek vengeance.

programme.title: Between Tears and Smiles
programme.desc: Fan Jia Shu is a kind-hearted student who is smitten with Shen, a heart-rending love song singer. However, he is not the only one who has eyes for Shen. The General’s henchmen are also determined to present the songstress to their superior as a gift. Fan receives help from an unexpected person just in time to save the woman he loves.

programme.title: Five Elements Ninjas
programme.desc: The "Venoms" were no more. After five years and more than a dozen films together, the only one of the original five who proved so successful for the director was the muscleman Lo Meng. But with just that one "venom" and his incredibly agile new star Cheng Tien-chi, he made this spectacular, internationally popular, favorite. Evil ninjas (who attack with, and from, fire, sun, wood, water, and the ground) brutally slaughter a noble Chinese kung-fu school's students. The one survivor finds a teacher and four students who are ninjitsu experts. The five graduates take revenge. With this strong structure and exceptional kung-fu choreography (from the star and co-star Chu Ke), Chang Cheh produced platinum. This film was one of the director's best of his superheroic, grand guignol period. By any name, it could be called, almost literally, "bloody good" entertainment!

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her father’s towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: The Black Lizard
programme.desc: Young swordsman Lung Fei encounters strange omens portending the death of his fiancé. His enquiries with the help of Chief Constable Tieh Hu reveal an astounding story, in this tale of men and women struggling to save their true loves.

programme.title: Lover's Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a man’s role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Roving Swordsman
programme.desc: An ambitious evil clan intends to rule the martial arts world. To achieve their goal, they must first steal a secret martial arts manuscript depicting how firearms can be produced. However, a supremely intelligent swordsman Shen Sheng Yi is protecting the manuscript and remains one step ahead of the evil clan.

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Tang Peng Nan are a sweet couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan at a time when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he found that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: The Fake Ghost Catchers
programme.desc: This delightful action comedy featuring international favourite Alexander Fu Sheng premiered two years before the American hit Ghostbusters was released. Is it a coincidence? You be the judge as you enjoy this amazing showcase of wushu and wizardry.

programme.title: Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers?
programme.desc: Jenny Hu, Shaw Brothers' gorgeous Chinese-German star, was given her first comedy role in the wild and wacky Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers? Described as "a comedy of belly laughs and chilling murders", it is a unique entry in the Hong Kong theater of the absurd.

programme.title: Killers Five
programme.desc: The Duke’s daughter has been kidnapped by the notorious Golden Dragon Hill bandits. A swordman named Yue Zhen Bei is assigned to save her, and expecting many dangers on the journey, Yue garners help from a group of good friends who are also kung fu masters.

programme.title: The Emperor and the Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperor’s plot once again.

programme.title: Clan Feuds
programme.desc: Like legendary director Chu Yuan did so often and so successfully, Chang Peng Yi adapted this film from a story by Ku Lung. Following the footsteps of the equally legendary Chang Cheh, Chang also casted the majestic Ti Lung, along with "Venoms” Lo Meng and Sun Chien, for a spectacular showcase of mystical Martial Arts World’s intrigue and consummate Kung Fu.

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: The Swift Knight
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor is dying with no heir to succeed the throne. His brother recalls that he has an illegitimate child with a court lady years ago and palace guards are sent to search for the heir. When the Emperor's nephew hires assassins to kill the child so he can be the successor, the Swift Knight comes to the rescue…

programme.title: Mist Over Dream Lake
programme.desc: A young girl Chen is sent away by her parents who are going through divorce, to stay with the Chang’s. On the Chang’s farm, she meets their two sons, the youngest daughter and a young artist, and spends a summer with them that she will never forget.

programme.title: The Rebel Intruders
programme.desc: Thousands of displaced refugees rush to the southern towns to avoid the civil war in north China. Three such young men trained with martial arts skills become sworn brothers, and accidentally got involved in the battle of the rebel leaders in town when they save a refugee girl. Can they fight back against the rebel gangs?

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: The Mad Monk is up against the equally legendary scholar-turned-genie, Lu Tung Pin. The duo create havoc as they vie with each other, be it in mirth, magic, women or weapons!

programme.title: The Fighting Fool
programme.desc: It's Meng Yuan-wen (star of The Master Strikes) versus Kuan Feng in this wild and wacky wushu saga of a priceless pole with a spectacular secret. A master martial artist's silly disciple struggles to save it from an evil white slaver, the slaver's duplicitous wife, and even his own bone-headed, but greedy, companion. Hsu Hsia choreographs the abundant action, as he had for both Five Superfighters and Drunken Master. The result is both sublime (for its kung-fu) and engagingly ridiculous.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back…

programme.title: Tales of a Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu Chia-hui, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chan's long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: The Dragon Missile
programme.desc: Sima works for a corrupt lord Qin who is suffering from a deadly disease that only a special herb can cure. Qin sends him on an urgent mission to retrieve it, but the task is made more difficult when Sima has to fight off other martial artists who want to steal the cure away from him. He has to fight with his ultimate weapon, the Dragon Missile!

programme.title: Irumbuthirai
programme.desc: Tamil Action Movie, Starring, Vishal, Samantha Akkineni, Arjun Sarja, Sreeja Ravi & others

programme.title: Thumbaa
programme.desc: Tamil adventure film, Starring, Dheena, Keerthi Pandian, Ravi Raghave, Darshan, KPY Palani & Others

programme.desc: Inauguration - Picking up one year after the events of the final episode of "The Good Wife," an enormous financial scam has destroyed the reputation of a young lawyer, Maia Rindell, while simultaneously wiping out her mentor and godmother Diane Lockhart's savings. Forced out of Lockhart & Lee, they join Lucca Quinn at one of Chicago's preeminent law firms.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep2
programme.desc: First Week - Diane raises eyebrows while settling in as a new partner at Reddick, Boseman & Kolstad. Maia continues to deal with the repercussions of her family's Ponzi scheme. Lucca and Maia unexpectedly pick up a new case.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep3
programme.desc: The Schtup List - Adrian and Barbara face a cruel realization about a high profile client. While second chair to Diane on a case, Lucca is in for more than she bargained for thanks to the state’s attorney’s office’s golden boy, Colin Morello. Maia visits her father in prison.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep4
programme.desc: Henceforth Known As Property - Diane and Lucca represent an ovarian cancer survivor looking to obtain custody of her previously donated embryos. Maia is the victim of a fake social media account. Mike Kresteva pays a visit to Reddick, Boseman & Kolstad.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep5
programme.desc: Stoppable: Requiem For An Airdate - Lucca defends a TV writer-producer in a copyright infringement case with ties to the President of the United States. Mike Kresteva takes aim at Reddick, Boseman & Kolstad. Carrie Preston, Matthew Perry and John Benjamin Hickey guest star.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep6
programme.desc: Social Media And Its Discontents - After landing tech mogul Neil Gross as a new client, the firm is tasked with figuring out a way to combat hate speech on his social media platform. programme.title: The Good Fight Ep7
programme.desc: Not So Grand Jury - Mike Kresteva takes his case against Reddick, Boseman & Kolstad to a grand jury, but the firm devises a grand jury strategy of their own to hamper Kresteva’s efforts. Colin finds himself in an awkward position in court.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep8
programme.desc: Reddick Vs Boseman - Founding partner, Carl Reddick, makes a surprise return to the firm. A renowned local pastor needs the firm’s help in a legal matter that threatens to ruin his legacy. Lucca unexpectedly meets Colin’s parents. Meanwhile, Henry attempts to reconnect with Maia.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep9
programme.desc: Self Condemned - Diane and Adrian find themselves involved in another police brutality case, this time representing a surprising but familiar face, Colin Sweeney. Lucca represents Maia for her interview with a federal investigator seeking information on the Rindell scandal.

programme.title: The Good Fight Ep10
programme.desc: Chaos - Season finale. Diane takes on a new client who is accused of cyber-terrorism, resulting in unforeseen repercussions for the firm, especially Lucca. An accident brings Diane and Kurt together. Henry reveals new truths about the scandal to Maia.

programme.title: Baby Animals 2 - Joined at the Hip Ep4
programme.desc: The animal kingdom can be a harsh place, but some baby animals have a family ready to take care of their needs. Meet some of these adorable babies and their clans: a koala joey, European elk twins, a litter of Asian short-clawed otters, and black howler monkey youngsters.

programme.title: Baby Animals 2 - Ugly Cute Ep5
programme.desc: Not all baby animals are cute. Often, quirky physical traits are evolutionary adaptations that have helped a species survive. Visit four funny-looking youngsters, including a Baird tapir, two baby gelada baboons, an anteater and a Bactrian camel.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 - Growing Up Gibbon Ep1
programme.desc: Hoolock Gibbons are true specialists of the Indian Jungle. Living in close knit family groups, youngsters must spend up to 9 years learning all the skills required to survive alone. From finding food in unusual places, to avoiding dangerous predators and mastering the acrobatics required for a life in the trees, we follow Samar as he finally comes of age and takes his first step into the wild.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 - Land of the Secret Rhino Ep2
programme.desc: The grasslands of Northeast India are one of the most fertile habitats on earth. Hundreds of species of tall grass flourish here, allowing one of India’s most iconic creatures to thrive… the Greater One-horned Rhino. This is one of the last places on earth where this gentle giant survives. Rani, an adult female has just had a baby, Rajah. This young rhino calf is only 3-month-old and his mom is his teacher, for the first year and half of his life. Rajah has much to learn, as he gets to grips with the world around him and everything there is to know about being a rhino.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 - Wild Stallions of the Himalayas Ep3
programme.desc: The high altitude Ladakh plateau in northwest India is a land of extremes. The air is thin and the mountain landscape treacherous; winters are freezing, while summers are scorching hot. The Tibetan wild ass is king of these grasslands, and one old stallion has developed a way to stay one step ahead of his rivals. We follow Dorje as he shadows a herd of females and foals, from winter to summer, when he will get his chance to sire the next generation. But to win his prize he must eventually do battle with other stallions - all wanting his crown!

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand 1 - Wild Fortresses Ep3
programme.desc: In New Zealand, two wild fortresses protect the vulnerable native animals: One a remote island protected by a moat of saltwater, the other a hilltop citadel surrounded by a predator-proof barrier. This is the story of these delicate sanctuaries and the life that thrives within them.

programme.title: Alien Abyss 1 - Origin Stories Ep1
programme.desc: Get acquainted with an array of ocean oddballs and learn how billions of years’ worth of changes, from ice ages to asteroid strikes, have shaped their looks and skills. Meet blind worms who fish, walking sharks, tree-climbing crabs, and much more.

programme.title: Alien Abyss 1 - Allies and Adversaries Ep2
programme.desc: Feel the love in the strange-but-heartwarming partnerships between some of Earth’s oddest creatures. Dive deep to see strange animals, from snapping shrimp to wolf eels, offer a hand to their fellow ocean-going weirdos to ensure mutual survival.

programme.title: Alien Abyss 1 - The Next Generation Ep3
programme.desc: Channel your inner sci-fi fan and explore the bizarre mating rituals of the ocean’s most peculiar creatures. Learn how bloody battles for mates, gender bending and supersize litters of babies just might secure a next generation for these animals.

programme.desc: The sprawling primate family includes animals as different as monkeys, lemurs and humans. Follow primate babies to see how they bond with their mothers, learn to socialize, and adapt to an ever-changing environment.

programme.title: Ol Pejeta Diaries 3 - Riddles of the Dead Ep1
programme.desc: The Black Rhino is the most endangered species in the world and when they start dying in rapid success, Ol Pejeta brings their expertise to help figure out what’s killing them—before its too late.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 - A Sloth Bear's Dilemma Ep4
programme.desc: In a land of searing summer heat and thunderous tropical storms, life for all that live on the plains of southern India is tough. But this year it’s harder than ever as the monsoon rains are late to arrive. For Bibi, a female sloth bear with two young cubs, this will be the biggest challenge of her life. With no rainfall, food will be hard to find and her cubs are also open to attack from leopards and other bears. Bibi must guide her family through this tricky time. Does she have the experience for them all to survive?

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 - Rana: Queen of the Jungle Ep5
programme.desc: One of the most iconic animals on Earth stalks the jungles of India: the Bengal Tiger. Over the course of a single day, we follow the fortunes of one mother and her three young cubs. She must provide enough food for her family to stay alive.

programme.title: Into the Wild India 1 - Youngsters of the Desert Ep6
programme.desc: A young lion cub must survive as his family is torn apart; two adolescent leopard cubs must fend for themselves after they are abandoned, and a young adult blackbuck must risk life and limb as he tries to secure his first mating.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand 1 - Ocean Legacy Ep4
programme.desc: Spring on New Zealand’s east coast is a time of promise for the New Zealand Fur Seal and the Norther Royal Albatross. They’ve returned to their land to breed. But harsh terrain, fickle weather and hungry predators will conspire to make lives difficult for them. Only the strongest will survive to carry forward their legacy.

programme.title: Planet Shark 1 - Ultimate Predator Ep1
programme.desc: Stalk the seas with sharks as they hunt using heightened senses and killer instincts. Watch a whitetip reef shark put its electrical sensors to work finding its prey’s heartbeat, and the pelagic thresher shark stun its quarry with its whiplike tail.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 2 - Weatherproof Ep1
programme.desc: Steer clear of these alphas, whose horns, claws, and other protective gear keep them ready for battle, no matter what the weather dishes out. Examine killer Highland cow horns, plucky mallard bills, razor-edged wolverine claws, and more.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 2 - Agile Ep2
programme.desc: Check out some fancy footwork and killer alpha moves. Catch a male brown hare throwing punches at his beloved, admire a sandhill crane dance battle, watch ibexes butt heads (literally) during mating season, and see why leopards are stealth masters.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 2 - Social Ep3
programme.desc: Meet alphas who get by with a little help from their friends. Discover the inescapable gang mentality of mating male dolphins, ponder ant colonies’ unique scents, find out why female geladas always get the last word, and see wolves hunt family-style.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 2 - Scrappy Ep4
programme.desc: Celebrate small but mighty animal warriors armed with sheaves of scary weapons. Admire nutrias’ stink bombs; honey badgers’ savage, needle-like choppers; black-tailed gulls’ razor-sharp beaks; and the killer talons on dive-bombing peregrine falcons.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 2 - Pointy Bits Ep5
programme.desc: Avoid the swords, spikes, and deadly hood ornaments on these alpha hunters. Observe elands locking corkscrew horns, storks rattling sabre-shaped beaks, rhinos scaring the competition with massive horns, and striped marlins spearing unsuspecting prey.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 2 - Scroungers/Scavengers Ep6
programme.desc: Go scavenging with nature’s cleanup crew. See Tasmanian devils get into food fights with rivals; learn how dung beetles roll over the competition; view wild boars’ fierce mating strategies; and watch hyenas’ bone-crushing teeth demolish any meal.

programme.title: Shark Squad 1 - Island of the White Shark Ep1
programme.desc: Off Guadalupe Island, Mexico, top shark ecologist Mauricio Hoyos attempts a television first. Get a unique view as he attaches a camera to the dorsal fin of a great white, revealing how it swims, hunts, and ultimately strikes its prey.

programme.title: Shark Squad 1 - Bimini Sharklab Ep2
programme.desc: Travel to a remote part of the Bahamas to unlock shark secrets. Do they make friends? Where do they give birth? Are some bolder than others? The answers may help protect these supreme predators for generations to come.

programme.title: UFC 284: Makhachev vs. Volkanovski
programme.desc: Prelims - When the Octagon returns to Australia on February 12, a SuperFight will be on tap for the UFC 284 mainevent at RAC Arena in Perth, as newly-crowned lightweight champion Islam Makhachev defends his title for the first time against the undisputed eatherweight champion, Australia’s own Alexander Volkanovski. Looking to join the exclusive list of double-champs in UFC history, Volkanovski enters his first fight on home soil since 2018 on the heels of a dominant 145-pound reign that includes four successful title defenses over the likes of Max Holloway, Brian Ortega and Chan Sung Jung. But in February, he will be put to the test by Dagestan’s Makhachev, a dominant presence in his own right who extended his current winning streak to 11 in October when he submitted Charles Oliveira in the second round to win the 155-pound championship he will defend against Alexander “The Great”. Plus, the interim featherweight title will be on the line in the co-main event when top contenders Yair Rodriguez and Josh Emmett collide in what promises to an explosive five-round championship bout, and former world champion Robert Whittaker faces Paulo Cos
